reviewText: Newhart delivers some of his original Button Down stand-up bits; very funny stuff. It's not original material, this was a special made long after Newhart had become famous from his TV shows.

This DVD is a hodgepodge of several routines Newhart did back in the early part of his career, and most are abridged to allow him to get them all into the program.

The "Button down mind" CD's have the whole things.  Buy them- much better.
